reviewText: Very fast course but there was no participation needed, pretty straight foward and boring course. Need to add more content.

The course is designed to provide learners with a deep understanding of the marketing environment, both macro and micro, and to equip them with the skills necessary to design and implement effective marketing strategies.  The emphasis on research and application of key models and concepts is a great way to reinforce learning and ensure that students are able to gain a practical understanding of marketing strategy.  Overall, I would highly recommend this course to anyone looking to gain a solid foundation in marketing strategy and to develop the skills necessary to succeed in a competitive business environment.
